        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ", ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "I rescued",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ") Lysias is silent as to the scourging: ch. ",
