        "class": "",
        "text": "Rescued",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "p",
        "class": "",
        "text": "Bengel says, \"a lie.\" Lysias wishes to make the impression that Paul's citizenship was the cause of his rescuing him; whereas he did not know of this until afterward. He says nothing about the proposed scourging. ",
        "children": []
